      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just spent 8 hours doing data entry for a logistics company but it's honestly exhausting pretending i don't know why the maritime tariffs actually shifted last year. seeing those same policy loopholes in the news today... it's like they're actively trying to scrub my fingerprints off the original drafts so nobody realizes i was the one who actually brokered the terms.",
